DECAID PROJECT SETUP GUIDE
========================

🎯 Complete Guide to Run DECAID Project in VS Code
==================================================

📋 TABLE OF CONTENTS
--------------------
1. Project Overview
2. Prerequisites
3. VS Code Setup
4. Terminal Configuration
5. Startup Commands
6. Service Verification
7. Login Credentials
8. Troubleshooting
9. Stop Commands

🏗️ PROJECT OVERVIEW
-------------------
DECAID = Decentralized Academic Credentials Verification System

Components:
• Frontend (React + Vite) - Port 3000
• Backend (Node.js + Express) - Port 5000
• AI Service (FastAPI + Python) - Port 8000
• Blockchain (Hardhat + Solidity) - Port 8545

🔧 PREREQUISITES
-----------------
✅ Node.js (v16+) installed
✅ Python (v3.8+) installed
✅ VS Code installed
✅ Project folder: E:\FinalYearProject

🖥️ VS CODE SETUP
-----------------

Step 1: Open Project
------------------
1. Open VS Code
2. Open Terminal: Ctrl + Shift + ` (backtick)
3. Navigate to project:
   cd E:\FinalYearProject

Step 2: Open 5 Terminals
-------------------------
Press Ctrl + Shift + ` 5 times to create 5 separate terminals
Each terminal will run one service

📋 TERMINAL COMMANDS
---------------------

🔌 TERMINAL 1: BLOCKCHAIN NETWORK
----------------------------------
cd E:\FinalYearProject\blockchain
npx hardhat node --hostname 127.0.0.1 --port 8545

Expected Output:
"Started HTTP and WebSocket JSON-RPC server"

🏗️ TERMINAL 2: DEPLOY SMART CONTRACT
------------------------------------
cd E:\FinalYearProject\blockchain
npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network localhost

Expected Output:
"CredentialRegistry deployed to: 0x5FbDB2315678afecb367f032d93F642f64180aa3"

🤖 TERMINAL 3: AI SERVICE
----------------------------
cd E:\FinalYearProject\ai-service
python -c "import uvicorn; from main import app; uvicorn.run(app, host='127.0.0.1', port=8000)"

Expected Output:
"Uvicorn running on http://127.0.0.1:8000"

⚙️ TERMINAL 4: BACKEND API
----------------------------
cd E:\FinalYearProject\backend
npm run dev

Expected Output:
"Backend listening on http://127.0.0.1:5000"

🌐 TERMINAL 5: FRONTEND
-------------------------
cd E:\FinalYearProject\frontend
npm run dev

Expected Output:
"Local: http://localhost:3000"

🚀 STARTUP ORDER (IMPORTANT)
----------------------------
1️⃣ FIRST: Terminal 1 (Blockchain Network)
   Wait for "Started HTTP and WebSocket JSON-RPC server"

2️⃣ SECOND: Terminal 2 (Deploy Contract)
   Wait for "CredentialRegistry deployed to: 0x5FbDB..."

3️⃣ THIRD: Terminal 3 (AI Service)
   Wait for "Uvicorn running on http://127.0.0.1:8000"

4️⃣ FOURTH: Terminal 4 (Backend)
   Wait for "Backend listening on http://127.0.0.1:5000"

5️⃣ FIFTH: Terminal 5 (Frontend)
   Wait for "Local: http://localhost:3000"

