✅ SERVICE VERIFICATION
----------------------
Check these URLs to verify all services:

Frontend:     http://localhost:3000
Backend API:   http://localhost:5000/health
AI Service:    http://localhost:8000/docs
Blockchain:     http://localhost:8545

📊 QUICK COPY-PASTE COMMANDS
----------------------------

Terminal 1 (Blockchain):
cd E:\FinalYearProject\blockchain && npx hardhat node --hostname 127.0.0.1 --port 8545

Terminal 2 (Deploy):
cd E:\FinalYearProject\blockchain && npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.js --network localhost

Terminal 3 (AI Service):
cd E:\FinalYearProject\ai-service && python -c "import uvicorn; from main import app; uvicorn.run(app, host='127.0.0.1', port=8000)"

Terminal 4 (Backend):
cd E:\FinalYearProject\backend && npm run dev

Terminal 5 (Frontend):
cd E:\FinalYearProject\frontend && npm run dev

🛑 STOP ALL SERVICES
--------------------
To stop all services:
taskkill /F /IM node.exe
taskkill /F /IM python.exe

🔧 TROUBLESHOOTING
-------------------

Issue: Port already in use
Solution: Stop services with taskkill commands above

Issue: Blockchain not responding
Solution: Restart Terminal 1 and Terminal 2

Issue: AI service not starting
Solution: Check Python installation, restart Terminal 3

Issue: Backend not connecting to blockchain
Solution: Verify contract deployment in Terminal 2

Issue: Frontend not loading
Solution: Check if backend is running in Terminal 4

